title: I Survived 100 Days as a WARPED PIGLIN in Hardcore Minecraft... Here’s What Happened
author: Corinthius
description:

In this video, I attempted to survive 100 days in hardcore minecraft as a warped piglin! I come from a different universe where the piglins evolved in the warped forest instead of the crimson forest. Now there is a clash between worlds and all out war with red vs blue. I used the shapeshifter or morph mod in survival minecraft.
